To start the program do the following:

1 - Open two terminals at this directory: Desktop/llm-voicechat-demo/Code


2 - Activate the "voicebot" environment in both terminals:
    """
    conda activate voicebot
    """

3 - Run the backend in one terminal:
    """
    python FlaskSocketIO_backend.py
    """
4 - Run the GUI in the other terminal:
    """
    python FlaskSocketIO_GUI.py
    """

5 - Make sure that the backend is fully loaded before clicking on "Starte Gespr채ch".
    The backend is fully loaded when it ouputs:
    """
    * Serving Flask app 'FlaskSocketIO_backend'
    * Debug mode: off
    """




